1
00:00:44,840 --> 00:00:46,440
To compete for the Leo route,

2
00:00:47,280 --> 00:00:49,720
we have to go against the Ou family of Siam Group,

3
00:00:49,720 --> 00:00:51,520
but we have no chance of winning.

4
00:00:53,120 --> 00:00:55,380
Since Mr. Ou proposed joint development

5
00:00:55,760 --> 00:00:56,760
and a 50-50 split,

6
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:58,600
it's not a bad strategy.

7
00:00:58,800 --> 00:00:59,520
Uncle Chen.

8
00:01:02,640 --> 00:01:03,300
Uncle Chen.

9
00:01:04,280 --> 00:01:05,209
Long time no see.

10
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:10,520
I just heard someone mention a strategy.

11
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:12,400
Back when my grandfather

12
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:14,320
founded the Sihai Group,

13
00:01:14,320 --> 00:01:16,960
he didn't even share the sea breeze with anyone.

14
00:01:16,960 --> 00:01:20,320
Since when do we rely on profit-sharing to survive?

15
00:01:22,160 --> 00:01:23,720
You're just a playboy.

16
00:01:24,160 --> 00:01:26,560
Doing business isn't about talking tough.

17
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:27,340
Get out!

18
00:01:30,080 --> 00:01:30,740
Don't move!

19
00:01:31,880 --> 00:01:34,720
I'm a veteran who built this empire with your father.

20
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:35,759
How dare you treat me like this!

21
00:01:35,759 --> 00:01:38,360
I think you're just flaunting your seniority.

22
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:42,840
Monopolizing the Leo route,

23
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,860
and eliminating dissidents.

24
00:01:45,160 --> 00:01:45,960
Ang Wei.

25
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:49,920
You sure talk big.

26
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:52,120
Can you handle it?

27
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:54,530
I forgot.

28
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:56,840
Back then, for the sake of profit,

29
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:59,370
you killed the shipping magnate's daughter,

30
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:00,250
Dailing.

31
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:03,480
He wouldn't even spare the woman he loves.

32
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:05,140
Mr. Chen, you must be careful.

33
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,850
You conspired with Siam Group.

34
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,800
Are you disrespecting Sihai

35
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,800
or disrespecting me?

36
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:30,400
I call the shots for Sihai Group.

37
00:02:30,720 --> 00:02:32,440
You old farts, shut up.

38
00:02:32,640 --> 00:02:33,840
I'll negotiate the flight route.

39
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,240
This kid is too arrogant.

40
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:40,360
Let's go.

41
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:46,280
In two days,

42
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:47,960
Biyang will be at Tan Palace.

43
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:49,090
I'll go meet him.

44
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:15,320
Mr. Biyang.

45
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:15,800
Sir.

46
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,240
I'm right here!

47
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:34,440
Leave through the back door.

48
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:35,640
I'll cover your escape.

49
00:03:35,640 --> 00:03:36,770
We'll meet up later.

50
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:58,200
Young Master,

51
00:03:58,640 --> 00:03:59,700
Mr. Biyang is dead.

52
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:01,900
Over there.

53
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:12,960
Angwei.

54
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,040
Go take a look.

55
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:35,440
Dailing.

56
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:23,800
Did they take the bait?

57
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:24,760
They took the bait.

58
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:26,620
Remember rule 25 of the boot camp.

59
00:05:26,640 --> 00:05:28,240
Never show mercy to enemies.

60
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:29,640
Ever.

61
00:06:11,960 --> 00:06:12,760
Are you crazy?

62
00:06:13,080 --> 00:06:14,280
Why did you cut me off?

63
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,120
Dailing.

64
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:18,880
What Dailing?

65
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:27,400
Who are you?

66
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:33,600
If you want to know someone's name,

67
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:34,930
this isn't the right way

68
00:06:35,400 --> 00:06:36,240
to ask,

69
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:37,610
Mr. Chen.

70
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:40,440
You know me.

71
00:06:41,080 --> 00:06:42,720
The famous Mr. Chen.

72
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:44,520
Who doesn't know you?

73
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,080
Since you know me,

74
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:49,400
you should know

75
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:51,600
that people who lie to me don't end up well.

76
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,400
Who are you?

77
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:54,980
What's your name, and where are you from?

78
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:57,480
Is a name that important to you?

79
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:03,370
But since you want to know so badly,

80
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,920
remember it well.

81
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:12,280
My name is Feifei.

82
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:24,040
All right.

83
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:25,140
Almost.

84
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:26,800
Let me see.

85
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:30,200
Your turn.

86
00:07:57,760 --> 00:07:58,420
Don't move.

87
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:11,920
That's not right.

88
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:13,960
There was clearly a tattoo here.

89
00:08:20,440 --> 00:08:21,640
Have you seen enough?

90
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:26,120
I'm off work.

91
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:29,250
I sell my art, not my body, Master Chen.

92
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:57,680
Who exactly are you?

93
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:07,560
You carried me back here,

94
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:09,680
just to ask me this?

95
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,600
I thought

96
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:16,560
you wanted to do something else.

97
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:30,100
Where are you from?

98
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:32,180
Biancheng.

99
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:35,450
What are you doing in Mancheng?

100
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:38,600
Tan Palace is the liveliest place in Mancheng,

101
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:41,330
and a gathering place for young noblemen.

102
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:43,600
You brought me back here

103
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:46,480
because you like me, didn't you?

104
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:53,370
Have a drink.

105
00:10:16,160 --> 00:10:17,420
You look a lot like her,

106
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,520
but you are not her.

107
00:10:28,760 --> 00:10:30,680
If you like it,

108
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:33,840
you can also call me Dailing.

109
00:10:45,040 --> 00:10:45,840
Dailing.
